-- Goldman to pay $67 mln, Bain to pay $54 mln to settle LBO collusion lawsuit
-- 
-- Wed Jun 11, 2014 05:15PM EDT
-- None



June 11 (Reuters) - Goldman Sachs Group Inc <GS.N>:  * Agrees to pay $67 million, and bain capital partners agrees to pay $54    million, to settle lbo collusion lawsuit -- court records  * Goldman, bain deny wrongdoing in agreeing to settle -- court records  * Goldman, bain preliminary settlements disclosed in filings with U.S. district    court in Boston, and requires court approval  ((New York Equities Desk; tel: +1 646 223 6000))  ((For more news about Goldman Sachs Group Inc click here: [GS.N]))

